Let’s keep working hard starting tomorrow, Chisato-chan!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Oh, look!\nThere’s already so much buzz on social media!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event257-06-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Whoa, really? Let me see, let me see!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"‘The dance was so much fun! I hope they do it at a live concert too!’\n‘Can’t believe Pastel＊Palettes made it through... They’re this round’s dark horse!’\n‘Could they beat the favorites and take the championship? I’m rooting for them!’","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Oh, even the ViVidCanvas team sent a message!\n‘Congratulations on clearing the third round!\nWe’re cheering for Pastel*Palettes on your road to the Budokan!’ ...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event257-06-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ugh... Seeing so many people cheering for us...\nI’m just so happy~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"cry03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Oh! Aya-chan’s full-on emotional moment—it’s been a while since we’ve seen that!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Haha, well, it’s been a tough road to get here.\nI guess she finally let her guard down a little.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event257-06-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ugh, sorry.\nI told myself I’d save the tears for the very end~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"cry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"It’s okay to cry when you need to.\nThat’s just the kind of idol you are, Maruyama.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"You know, Ayumi was like that too.\nShe’d cry all the time, but every time she did, she’d come back stronger.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Haha... That really brings back memories...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Nao-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"You know, watching everyone face this challenge head-on...\nit reminded me of when I was in Marmalade.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Back then, we hit so many walls, over and over again.\nBut no matter what, we were determined to make it to the Budokan—\ntogether, with our members and our staff.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"I used to have that same feeling too.\nBut as I grew up and became a producer,\nI guess I forgot about it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"When I was performing, what meant the most to me was having adults around us\nwho would give their all and run alongside us.\nThat’s what made me happiest...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"But somewhere along the line, I forgot something so simple.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"I thought that, as someone who quit being an idol, I had to be the one pointing you toward the right path, guiding you away from anything risky.\nI got so stubborn about it... I kept pointing, but I never really stood beside you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"I’ve said unreasonable things, and I’ve been pushy at times.\nI know I haven’t been the best producer.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Even now, I don’t think being an idol is all sunshine and roses.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"I still believe you shouldn’t carry too many expectations on your shoulders.\nAnd I know we’ll probably clash again in the future... but still...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"I want to be someone you can rely on.\nThat feeling hasn’t changed.\nSo... let me keep doing my best alongside you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Nao-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Um... There were times when I was surprised by your decisions, Nao-san,\nand even felt uncertain about them.\nBut now, I understand they were things we needed.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event257-06-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Yes! Even when your words were harsh,\nI know they came from a place of care for us.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event257-06-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"There were definitely moments when I thought,\n'Wow, this doesn’t feel fun at all,' but...\nthere were just as many fun moments too!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Exactly. Without you, Nao-san,\nthere are so many sights we never would’ve seen.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event257-06-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"And, I don’t think trust is only about relying on someone completely.\nIt comes in different forms, after all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event257-06-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"We’re a ‘team’ with you too, Nao-san.\nSo please, keep working with us moving forward!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Everyone...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Thank you. I’ll keep doing my best with you all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Pastel＊Palettes","body":"Please take care of us!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event257-06-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Oh, I’ve got an idea!\nHow about we celebrate our win with a toast?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event257-06-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Good idea!\nAnd hey, we just bought some juice earlier!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Here you go, Nao-san. This one’s for you!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Oh, thanks.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"...Wait, isn’t that the soda you dropped earlier—?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya & Nao","body":"Huh?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event257-06-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":1,"soundReferenceIdx":3,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya & Nao","body":"Wahhhh!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event257-06-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"A-Are you okay?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event257-06-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"No, I’m not okay!\nI’m completely soaked—this is ridiculous~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Haha, you two got covered in soda together—it’s like a celebratory toast!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Nao-san, I’m so sorry!\nI didn’t think it would turn out like this!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"...Unforgivable.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Huh?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Unforgivable, Maruyama~!\nCome here—you’re not getting away~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"kime02","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Wahhh! It’s not my fault, I swear~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Aya-san, you’re incredible!\nAfter all that dancing, you still have so much energy!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event257-06-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Go, Aya-chan!\nNao-san doesn’t have much stamina, so drag this out—it’s your win!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event257-06-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"Hey, Hikawa...!\nWho said I don’t have stamina...?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Huh, are you already getting tired...?\nAlright, both of you, do your best~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event257-06-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Geez, don’t overdo it too much,\nor you might trip and fall.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event257-06-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ughhh, come on, someone help me~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event257-06-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina, Eve & Maya","body":"Hahaha!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"event257-06-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"(I want to say everything I can, do everything I can,\nto light the way forward for these kids, to be their guide.\nSo none of them ever have to cry with empty eyes.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"Nao","body":"(Because more than anything,\nI want them to always keep smiling.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event257-06-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0}],"selectableData":[],"layoutData":[{"type":2,"sideFrom":4